  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>A unique 2D precision platformer game in which you control an alien shepherd that goes looking for a missing sheep.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/fc85f75f8f0c0dadcd6e1d1d31c44a1c.poster.avif?t=1645954338\" width=600 height=580 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/fc85f75f8f0c0dadcd6e1d1d31c44a1c.webm?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/fc85f75f8f0c0dadcd6e1d1d31c44a1c.mp4?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> More than 50 different levels with increasing difficulty<br></li><li> Two game modes (normal/hard) to please casual and hardcore players<br></li><li> Oldschool handcrafted pixel-art<br></li><li> A unique mechanic that allows flying in any direction for a short period of time<br></li><li> A cute pet jellyfish</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/17920583fcd8bb2f3b775cd0fd192e93.poster.avif?t=1645954338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/17920583fcd8bb2f3b775cd0fd192e93.webm?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/17920583fcd8bb2f3b775cd0fd192e93.mp4?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><br>A unique 2D precision platformer game in which you control an alien shepherd that goes looking for a missing sheep.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/fc85f75f8f0c0dadcd6e1d1d31c44a1c.poster.avif?t=1645954338\" width=600 height=580 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/fc85f75f8f0c0dadcd6e1d1d31c44a1c.webm?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/fc85f75f8f0c0dadcd6e1d1d31c44a1c.mp4?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> More than 50 different levels with increasing difficulty<br></li><li> Two game modes (normal/hard) to please casual and hardcore players<br></li><li> Oldschool handcrafted pixel-art<br></li><li> A unique mechanic that allows flying in any direction for a short period of time<br></li><li> A cute pet jellyfish</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/17920583fcd8bb2f3b775cd0fd192e93.poster.avif?t=1645954338\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/17920583fcd8bb2f3b775cd0fd192e93.webm?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1808820/extras/17920583fcd8bb2f3b775cd0fd192e93.mp4?t=1645954338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
